          "plain_text": "I wake up the the sound of the ocean and a light rain. I excitedly open up the back of the canopy and look out over the beautiful yellow sands mouth. There are fun little waves! It’s not enormous, just far more consistent than last night. Health-wise I’m feeling almost 100% again which is lovely. ",
