    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I go check Nahoon and it’s pretty good. I have mixed feelings about this as I’m feeling pretty tired. I watch where people get out and in and the head off to get some lunch and a coffee. I’ve decided to spend another night in east London as there should be waves here again tomorrow. Maybe I’ll go and do a hike on Friday? ",
            "link": null
          },
